tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE session_tracking (
    session_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    start_time TIMESTAMP,
    end_time TIMESTAMP,
    duration INT
);

CREATE TABLE interaction_log (
    log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    interaction_type STRING,
    interaction_time TIMESTAMP,
    interaction_details STRING
);

CREATE TABLE location_tracking (
    location_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    latitude FLOAT,
    longitude FLOAT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE users (
    user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    username VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    email VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    avatar_url VARCHAR(255),
    created_at TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE sessions (
    session_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT REFERENCES users(user_id),
    session_duration INTERVAL NOT NULL,
    session_date DATE NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT session_user_id_unique UNIQUE (user_id, session_date)
);

CREATE TABLE interactions (
    interaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    session_id INT REFERENCES sessions(session_id),
    interaction_type VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL,
    interaction_timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    interaction_data VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE objects (
    object_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    object_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    object_type VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL,
    object_description TEXT,
    object_creator_id INT REFERENCES users(user_id)
);
